Node js developer

Objective:
Candidates can look forward to opportunity for software development and engineering as a role in mission-critical software development team including:
Responsibilities :
understanding mission-critical telecom software requirements;
assisting in design and engineering;
determining project deliverables;
full stack software development;
engineering back end applications;
front end application development;
deliveries as per project milestones.
Skills/Experience:
understanding and experience of telecom standards preferred;
experience on SIP, telephony stack development;
Good communication skills;
A keen grasp of information technology;
Professional demeanor;
Personal accountability and strong work ethic;
Professional, able to interact with vendors/clients;
Positive, “can do” attitude.
